item.description:
Join us for a fall weekend camping trip at Pawtuckaway State Park and bring your canoes, kayaks or other paddle sports toys. We'll be camping on Horse Island at Pawtuckaway and then spending the day on the water on Saturday where a group paddle is scheduled with those who do not plan on camping.

Note: After Columbus Day sites are available only on a Walk Up or First Come First Serve basis at the Park Visitors Office. If you plan to join us please plan on being there early Friday evening to insure a campsite on Horse Island.

Pawtuckaway State Park Campground Map

Campsite Reservations for Pawtuckaway State Park

For those camping we'll have a Pot Luck dinner Saturday night then relax by a group campfire. This is a great opportunity to talk about all the fun events we've had over the season and talk about future paddling events.

More info. to come closer to the event date.
item.name: Camping and Canoe/Kayaking Weekend at Pawtuckaway State Park
